<font color="yellow">(The following content may not be suitable for viewers under 15.)</font>

2
00:00:03,300 --> 00:00:05,600
<font color="yellow">(Viewer discretion is advised.)</font>

3
00:00:07,268 --> 00:00:09,208
<font color="yellow">(Episode 10)</font>

4
00:00:24,338 --> 00:00:25,438
<font color="yellow">Dad.</font>

5
00:00:39,352 --> 00:00:40,922
<font color="yellow">It's been a long while.</font>

6
00:01:00,422 --> 00:01:01,952
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry, Dad.</font>

7
00:01:02,982 --> 00:01:04,122
<font color="yellow">Forgive me.</font>

8
00:01:07,382 --> 00:01:08,492
<font color="yellow">I was...</font>

9
00:01:10,492 --> 00:01:12,052
<font color="yellow">I was a terrible son.</font>

10
00:01:13,852 --> 00:01:16,722
<font color="yellow">I didn't know you were sick. I was selfish.</font>

11
00:01:19,582 --> 00:01:21,482
<font color="yellow">I'm the worst.</font>

12
00:01:29,152 --> 00:01:30,652
<font color="yellow">It's not your fault.</font>

13
00:01:32,922 --> 00:01:34,852
<font color="yellow">I can still see,</font>

14
00:01:35,722 --> 00:01:37,882
<font color="yellow">and I can still move freely.</font>

15
00:01:38,452 --> 00:01:42,552
<font color="yellow">And I kept it a secret because I wanted to sort things out myself.</font>

16
00:01:44,552 --> 00:01:46,482
<font color="yellow">You must have looked into it,</font>

17
00:01:46,852 --> 00:01:50,382
<font color="yellow">but what I have can't be treated or cured.</font>

18
00:01:51,282 --> 00:01:52,582
<font color="yellow">If it can't be done here,</font>

19
00:01:53,322 --> 00:01:55,722
<font color="yellow">we can go abroad and get help there.</font>

20
00:01:55,952 --> 00:01:59,252
<font color="yellow">Our eyes grow dim with age and our hearing weakens.</font>

21
00:01:59,252 --> 00:02:01,282
<font color="yellow">It happens to us all.</font>

22
00:02:01,482 --> 00:02:02,622
<font color="yellow">It's nothing.</font>

23
00:02:02,952 --> 00:02:06,522
<font color="yellow">It's not worth making a fuss about.</font>

24
00:02:07,452 --> 00:02:08,582
<font color="yellow">I'm a man.</font>

25
00:02:10,322 --> 00:02:11,452
<font color="yellow">Dad.</font>

26
00:02:26,952 --> 00:02:28,352
<font color="yellow">How is your mum?</font>

27
00:02:29,452 --> 00:02:31,452
<font color="yellow">She was worried at first,</font>

28
00:02:32,022 --> 00:02:33,222
<font color="yellow">but now,</font>

29
00:02:34,022 --> 00:02:36,352
<font color="yellow">she wants you to return after fulfilling your wish.</font>

30
00:02:38,022 --> 00:02:39,522
<font color="yellow">She still worries, though.</font>

31
00:02:40,392 --> 00:02:42,392
<font color="yellow">She wonders if you eat regularly,</font>

32
00:02:43,052 --> 00:02:44,682
<font color="yellow">if you sleep in comfort,</font>

33
00:02:45,052 --> 00:02:48,222
<font color="yellow">and if you have enough money with you.</font>

34
00:02:48,852 --> 00:02:50,282
<font color="yellow">I'll return home soon.</font>

35
00:02:51,282 --> 00:02:53,522
<font color="yellow">So tell her not to worry too much.</font>

36
00:02:54,252 --> 00:02:56,782
<font color="yellow">Tell her she can relax.</font>

37
00:02:57,182 --> 00:03:00,382
<font color="yellow">Why don't you just come home with me tonight?</font>

38
00:03:00,482 --> 00:03:02,052
<font color="yellow">I'm almost done.</font>

39
00:03:02,722 --> 00:03:05,052
<font color="yellow">I'll come home when I'm finished.</font>

40
00:03:06,182 --> 00:03:10,282
<font color="yellow">- Mum and Dong Sook should know... - It's no rush.</font>

41
00:03:11,482 --> 00:03:14,252
<font color="yellow">- I'll tell them when I get back. - Dad.</font>

42
00:03:14,452 --> 00:03:17,622
<font color="yellow">Them finding out about my illness won't change anything.</font>

43
00:03:18,782 --> 00:03:20,682
<font color="yellow">Please keep it a secret...</font>

44
00:03:21,152 --> 00:03:25,452
<font color="yellow">until I come home and tell them myself.</font>

45
00:03:26,182 --> 00:03:27,582
<font color="yellow">Do me a favour.</font>

46
00:03:31,882 --> 00:03:35,122
<font color="yellow">Did you sell the tailor shop?</font>

47
00:03:36,052 --> 00:03:39,382
<font color="yellow">Sam Do decided to take over.</font>

48
00:03:39,822 --> 00:03:41,182
<font color="yellow">He started working today.</font>

49
00:03:42,152 --> 00:03:44,382
<font color="yellow">- Sam Do? - Yes.</font>

50
00:03:45,482 --> 00:03:47,152
<font color="yellow">After you left home,</font>

51
00:03:47,752 --> 00:03:52,182
<font color="yellow">he worried more than I did about you and about the store.</font>

52
00:03:52,782 --> 00:03:54,222
<font color="yellow">I owe him a lot.</font>

53
00:03:55,322 --> 00:03:57,352
<font color="yellow">He's a very rare man.</font>

54
00:04:03,122 --> 00:04:04,682
<font color="yellow">I was quite surprised.</font>

55
00:04:05,952 --> 00:04:07,322
<font color="yellow">I never imagined...</font>

56
00:04:08,322 --> 00:04:11,152
<font color="yellow">you'd be so calm and relaxed.</font>

57
00:04:12,682 --> 00:04:15,482
<font color="yellow">Aren't you afraid or frightened?</font>

58
00:04:16,382 --> 00:04:19,952
<font color="yellow">For a tailor to lose his sight...</font>

59
00:04:20,322 --> 00:04:22,382
<font color="yellow">is like a death sentence.</font>

60
00:04:23,122 --> 00:04:25,982
<font color="yellow">Of course I felt all sorts of emotions.</font>

61
00:04:27,522 --> 00:04:30,722
<font color="yellow">I was afraid and frightened.</font>

62
00:04:32,482 --> 00:04:36,652
<font color="yellow">But then again, I thought about it for a while.</font>

63
00:04:37,482 --> 00:04:38,692
<font color="yellow">My whole life,</font>

64
00:04:39,052 --> 00:04:42,692
<font color="yellow">I got to see all the greatest suits in the world.</font>

65
00:04:44,522 --> 00:04:47,622
<font color="yellow">My eyes saw many beautiful things.</font>

66
00:04:49,582 --> 00:04:53,352
<font color="yellow">I guess the world is just telling me that I've seen enough.</font>

67
00:04:54,252 --> 00:04:56,482
<font color="yellow">I saw more than enough,</font>

68
00:04:56,882 --> 00:05:01,282
<font color="yellow">so now I've been given time to prepare for the end.</font>

69
00:05:03,322 --> 00:05:04,552
<font color="yellow">That's why...</font>

70
00:05:06,252 --> 00:05:10,152
<font color="yellow">I'm doing what I considered doing for a long time.</font>

71
00:05:11,482 --> 00:05:15,422
<font color="yellow">You have no idea how nice it is to be able to put my life in order.</font>

72
00:05:16,922 --> 00:05:19,122
<font color="yellow">I know you're making suits for the less fortunate.</font>

73
00:05:19,122 --> 00:05:23,352
<font color="yellow">But you can do that from home. I will help you.</font>

74
00:05:23,352 --> 00:05:27,252
<font color="yellow">This is something I have to do alone.</font>

75
00:05:31,852 --> 00:05:35,282
<font color="yellow">If I were to say I wanted to continue the family business,</font>

76
00:05:36,052 --> 00:05:37,182
<font color="yellow">would that make you happy?</font>

77
00:05:37,382 --> 00:05:39,052
<font color="yellow">I've given up on that.</font>

78
00:05:40,752 --> 00:05:43,552
<font color="yellow">I don't want you to continue the family business.</font>

79
00:05:45,052 --> 00:05:47,782
<font color="yellow">I want you to do what you want.</font>

80
00:05:48,652 --> 00:05:52,382
<font color="yellow">To be honest, I don't know what I want...</font>

81
00:05:53,182 --> 00:05:55,282
<font color="yellow">or what I should do that will...</font>

82
00:05:56,222 --> 00:05:57,482
<font color="yellow">make me happy.</font>

83
00:06:01,752 --> 00:06:04,852
<font color="yellow">I know this much about you, my son.</font>

84
00:06:06,252 --> 00:06:08,352
<font color="yellow">You aren't a fool who would give up...</font>

85
00:06:08,682 --> 00:06:12,022
<font color="yellow">something valuable so you could succeed or gain fame.</font>

86
00:06:13,622 --> 00:06:15,422
<font color="yellow">Will you promise me something?</font>

87
00:06:16,282 --> 00:06:17,982
<font color="yellow">Promise me that...</font>

88
00:06:18,922 --> 00:06:21,722
<font color="yellow">by the time I return home, you will have found...</font>

89
00:06:22,582 --> 00:06:24,552
<font color="yellow">what makes you happy.</font>

90
00:06:27,582 --> 00:06:29,552
<font color="yellow">When I grow up,</font>

91
00:06:29,552 --> 00:06:32,222
<font color="yellow">I'll make you a suit, too. I promise.</font>

92
00:06:32,422 --> 00:06:35,622
<font color="yellow">You make promises with a lot of other people with your pinky,</font>

93
00:06:35,922 --> 00:06:38,722
<font color="yellow">so make your promise to me with your thumb.</font>

94
00:06:46,982 --> 00:06:50,222
<font color="yellow">This is how we make promises.</font>

95
00:07:12,222 --> 00:07:13,922
<font color="yellow">- Hello. - Where are you?</font>

96
00:07:14,122 --> 00:07:15,622
<font color="yellow">I said I'd drive you.</font>

97
00:07:15,852 --> 00:07:17,582
<font color="yellow">It's just a short taxi ride.</font>

98
00:07:18,122 --> 00:07:19,952
<font color="yellow">- Dong Jin. - Yes?</font>

99
00:07:20,282 --> 00:07:22,182
<font color="yellow">Keep your promise.</font>

100
00:07:22,652 --> 00:07:26,482
<font color="yellow">I believe that by the time I come home, you'll have found...</font>

101
00:07:28,122 --> 00:07:29,982
<font color="yellow">what you want to do...</font>

102
00:07:30,822 --> 00:07:33,052
<font color="yellow">and what you should do to make yourself happy.</font>

103
00:07:37,652 --> 00:07:39,652
<font color="yellow">Your uncle got a divorce?</font>

104
00:07:40,022 --> 00:07:43,122
<font color="yellow">- Are you sure? - Be quiet. Grandma might hear you.</font>

105
00:07:43,982 --> 00:07:46,152
<font color="yellow">Hyo Won told me this evening.</font>

106
00:07:48,552 --> 00:07:49,682
<font color="yellow">Who will you call?</font>

107
00:07:49,782 --> 00:07:52,222
<font color="yellow">Who do you think? I need to check.</font>

108
00:07:53,222 --> 00:07:56,482
<font color="yellow">Uncle Dong Jin must feel bad as it is. Leave him alone.</font>

109
00:07:57,582 --> 00:07:59,922
<font color="yellow">Why would they get a divorce?</font>

110
00:08:01,252 --> 00:08:02,882
<font color="yellow">Is your aunt seeing someone?</font>

111
00:08:02,882 --> 00:08:04,582
<font color="yellow">Stop it, Mum.</font>

112
00:08:06,022 --> 00:08:08,482
<font color="yellow">No? What else could it be?</font>

113
00:08:08,782 --> 00:08:11,652
<font color="yellow">- Is Da Jeong home? - You scared me.</font>

114
00:08:12,722 --> 00:08:16,122
<font color="yellow">Why are you so surprised? Were you two gossiping?</font>

115
00:08:17,022 --> 00:08:18,952
<font color="yellow">Why would we be gossiping?</font>

116
00:08:19,182 --> 00:08:22,252
<font color="yellow">We weren't expecting you to come out of the room so suddenly.</font>

117
00:08:22,582 --> 00:08:24,952
<font color="yellow">I didn't say hi because Mum said you were asleep.</font>

118
00:08:25,352 --> 00:08:26,482
<font color="yellow">I'm home.</font>

119
00:08:26,482 --> 00:08:30,182
<font color="yellow">I don't understand why I feel asleep so early today.</font>

120
00:08:33,052 --> 00:08:34,752
<font color="yellow">Where's the spinach soup?</font>

121
00:08:36,222 --> 00:08:38,322
<font color="yellow">- I forgot. - What a useless mum you are.</font>

122
00:08:39,292 --> 00:08:41,752
<font color="yellow">I'll warm the soup up for you.</font>

123
00:08:41,952 --> 00:08:45,022
<font color="yellow">- Wait a little bit. - Okay, Grandma.</font>

124
00:08:52,352 --> 00:08:55,292
<font color="yellow">- We should be careful. - You should be careful.</font>

125
00:08:56,722 --> 00:09:00,422
<font color="yellow">A little rat keeps stealing our food whenever he comes and goes.</font>

126
00:09:01,022 --> 00:09:02,752
<font color="yellow">I just can't dare leave the house.</font>

127
00:09:03,252 --> 00:09:05,122
<font color="yellow">Don't be so mean. It's just food.</font>

128
00:09:05,322 --> 00:09:07,882
<font color="yellow">I'm not one to complain about such issues,</font>

129
00:09:08,252 --> 00:09:10,382
<font color="yellow">but look at this. He ate over half the chicken.</font>

130
00:09:10,922 --> 00:09:13,292
<font color="yellow">He'd have eaten it all if I hadn't come up in time.</font>

131
00:09:13,292 --> 00:09:15,622
<font color="yellow">No wonder there's so little meat. I thought this was a chick.</font>

132
00:09:16,052 --> 00:09:17,882
<font color="yellow">The rat has a huge appetite.</font>

133
00:09:18,052 --> 00:09:21,752
<font color="yellow">I should get a few traps from the store tomorrow.</font>

134
00:09:23,322 --> 00:09:24,652
<font color="yellow">There's nothing but sauce left.</font>

135
00:09:30,582 --> 00:09:34,622
<font color="yellow">The chicken wasn't worth this kind of insult. Stupid me.</font>

136
00:09:35,152 --> 00:09:36,882
<font color="yellow">Just get married.</font>

137
00:09:37,322 --> 00:09:39,322
<font color="yellow">Eat your wife's cooking.</font>

138
00:09:39,522 --> 00:09:41,722
<font color="yellow">Leave our food alone.</font>

139
00:09:42,052 --> 00:09:44,292
<font color="yellow">Dong Sook's a great girl with just one flaw.</font>

140
00:09:44,482 --> 00:09:46,982
<font color="yellow">She can't cook to save her life.</font>

141
00:09:47,182 --> 00:09:49,052
<font color="yellow">They keep mentioning her.</font>

142
00:09:57,022 --> 00:09:58,922
<font color="yellow">- Are you glue? - What do you mean?</font>

143
00:09:58,922 --> 00:10:01,482
<font color="yellow">Why do you keep trying to stick me and Dong Sook together?</font>

144
00:10:01,482 --> 00:10:03,292
<font color="yellow">She isn't my type.</font>

145
00:10:04,052 --> 00:10:06,652
<font color="yellow">- What's so bad about her? - Exactly.</font>

146
00:10:07,122 --> 00:10:10,052
<font color="yellow">She's the one who should be rejecting you, you know.</font>

147
00:10:10,552 --> 00:10:12,652
<font color="yellow">- Dock it from the repair fee. - Dock what?</font>

148
00:10:13,152 --> 00:10:15,292
<font color="yellow">The price of the chicken stew.</font>

149
00:10:15,482 --> 00:10:18,052
<font color="yellow">Dock it from the 100 dollars you owe me this month.</font>

150
00:10:18,422 --> 00:10:21,422
<font color="yellow">Okay, then I'll wire you 70 dollars this month.</font>

151
00:10:26,382 --> 00:10:27,582
<font color="yellow">70 dollars?</font>

152
00:10:28,292 --> 00:10:31,322
<font color="yellow">Does that mean I ate 30 dollars' worth of chicken?</font>

153
00:10:31,982 --> 00:10:33,922
<font color="yellow">That's daylight robbery.</font>

154
00:10:34,022 --> 00:10:36,122
<font color="yellow">You're unarmed, but you're still a thief.</font>

155
00:10:37,182 --> 00:10:38,982
<font color="yellow">The chicken stew you had...</font>

156
00:10:39,052 --> 00:10:41,882
<font color="yellow">follows a recipe that came down from my great-grandmother,</font>

157
00:10:41,882 --> 00:10:45,122
<font color="yellow">and it also includes my own special and secret sauce.</font>

158
00:10:45,352 --> 00:10:47,352
<font color="yellow">You even said it was the best.</font>

159
00:10:47,552 --> 00:10:50,482
<font color="yellow">Even so, I didn't eat the whole chicken.</font>

160
00:10:50,682 --> 00:10:53,682
<font color="yellow">I only ate a drumstick and breast meat which was very dry.</font>

161
00:10:54,052 --> 00:10:56,282
<font color="yellow">You can't charge 30 dollars for that.</font>

162
00:10:56,652 --> 00:10:58,982
<font color="yellow">You made us pay 1,000 dollars to fix your guitar.</font>

163
00:10:59,482 --> 00:11:00,782
<font color="yellow">- That's robbery, too. - It is.</font>

164
00:11:00,982 --> 00:11:02,752
<font color="yellow">- I want a drumstick. - Okay.</font>

165
00:11:02,852 --> 00:11:07,322
<font color="yellow">You two are quite the team. Are you in this together now?</font>

166
00:11:08,852 --> 00:11:11,052
<font color="yellow">Hey. How could you do that?</font>

167
00:11:11,622 --> 00:11:13,852
<font color="yellow">You can't just steal the drumstick.</font>

168
00:11:13,952 --> 00:11:15,382
<font color="yellow">I don't want to eat it.</font>

169
00:11:15,852 --> 00:11:18,852
<font color="yellow">But I'm force-feeding myself to eat 30 dollars' worth of food.</font>

170
00:11:19,052 --> 00:11:20,322
<font color="yellow">It's not because it's tasty.</font>

171
00:11:20,522 --> 00:11:23,552
<font color="yellow">I don't believe this. How can someone be so shameless?</font>

172
00:11:24,022 --> 00:11:27,182
<font color="yellow">It's fine. I've had enough, and I lost my appetite anyway.</font>

173
00:11:27,382 --> 00:11:29,482
<font color="yellow">Leave it. Don't get angry over nothing.</font>

174
00:11:29,682 --> 00:11:31,282
<font color="yellow">- What a jerk. - Let's go inside.</font>

175
00:11:31,382 --> 00:11:32,422
<font color="yellow">This is unbelievable.</font>

176
00:11:33,422 --> 00:11:35,282
<font color="yellow">Finish up and do the dishes.</font>

177
00:11:36,282 --> 00:11:38,482
<font color="yellow">Let's go to bed, Honey.</font>

178
00:11:41,952 --> 00:11:43,052
<font color="yellow">My gosh.</font>

179
00:12:01,182 --> 00:12:04,352
<font color="yellow">Now, it's worth 30 dollars.</font>

180
00:12:28,822 --> 00:12:30,522
<font color="yellow">What are you doing? Get your face out of the way.</font>

181
00:12:30,622 --> 00:12:34,152
<font color="yellow">I saved your life. Shouldn't you at least thank me for it?</font>

182
00:12:34,352 --> 00:12:36,322
<font color="yellow">Do you really want to show off?</font>

183
00:12:36,422 --> 00:12:38,052
<font color="yellow">I'm not showing off.</font>

184
00:12:38,382 --> 00:12:42,022
<font color="yellow">You should thank your lifesaver. It's basic manners.</font>

185
00:12:42,122 --> 00:12:44,822
<font color="yellow">Okay, then. Thank you so much.</font>

186
00:12:47,952 --> 00:12:49,822
<font color="yellow">I still don't believe what he said.</font>

187
00:12:50,252 --> 00:12:53,182
<font color="yellow">I should've let him struggle in the water.</font>

188
00:12:55,982 --> 00:12:58,182
<font color="yellow">Why aren't you asleep?</font>

189
00:12:58,482 --> 00:13:00,882
<font color="yellow">You said you have to leave at dawn.</font>

190
00:13:01,182 --> 00:13:03,282
<font color="yellow">Sleep well, Mother.</font>

191
00:13:25,052 --> 00:13:27,122
<font color="yellow">Leave the scissors alone, Dong Jin.</font>

192
00:13:27,922 --> 00:13:29,222
<font color="yellow">You'll hurt yourself.</font>

193
00:13:33,582 --> 00:13:36,152
<font color="yellow">Shall we do it together, then?</font>

194
00:13:36,622 --> 00:13:37,622
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

195
00:13:37,622 --> 00:13:39,052
<font color="yellow">Hold it tight.</font>

196
00:13:40,182 --> 00:13:42,722
<font color="yellow">Let's begin.</font>

197
00:13:43,982 --> 00:13:46,922
<font color="yellow">Cut straight down.</font>

198
00:13:47,882 --> 00:13:50,452
<font color="yellow">In a straight line. That's it.</font>

199
00:13:50,722 --> 00:13:51,722
<font color="yellow">Well done.</font>

200
00:14:15,982 --> 00:14:18,782
<font color="yellow">I saw a happy little boy cutting through...</font>

201
00:14:18,782 --> 00:14:21,822
<font color="yellow">and playing around with leftover pieces of fabric.</font>

202
00:14:23,052 --> 00:14:25,222
<font color="yellow">I hadn't had such a nice dream in a while.</font>

203
00:14:31,152 --> 00:14:33,652
<font color="yellow">I left you to search for happiness, Dad.</font>

204
00:14:34,522 --> 00:14:37,982
<font color="yellow">But why do I think that I feel truly happy...</font>

205
00:14:38,382 --> 00:14:40,382
<font color="yellow">when I'm close to you?</font>

206
00:14:42,052 --> 00:14:46,022
<font color="yellow">Will I become happy, Dad, if I return to the store...</font>

207
00:14:46,822 --> 00:14:48,522
<font color="yellow">like I did in the dream?</font>

208
00:15:03,182 --> 00:15:04,782
<font color="yellow">How could you, Hyo Joo?</font>

209
