858
00:50:30,522 --> 00:50:32,522
<font color="yellow">I forgot to tell you something.</font>

859
00:50:32,882 --> 00:50:34,052
<font color="yellow">Starting next week,</font>

860
00:50:34,422 --> 00:50:36,922
