862
00:50:39,352 --> 00:50:40,582
<font color="yellow">You can't be serious.</font>

863
00:50:41,952 --> 00:50:44,222
<font color="yellow">Isn't he really smart and well-off?</font>

864
00:50:44,922 --> 00:50:47,282
