867
00:50:56,982 --> 00:50:58,582
<font color="yellow">Mr Lee isn't even here right now.</font>

868
00:50:58,882 --> 00:51:01,352
<font color="yellow">Why would he start this now?</font>

869
00:51:02,222 --> 00:51:04,322
