884
00:52:08,382 --> 00:52:12,722
<font color="yellow">once he starts working there. What should I do?</font>

885
00:52:20,822 --> 00:52:22,052
<font color="yellow">It's a thief!</font>

886
00:52:28,682 --> 00:52:30,182
<font color="yellow">- Why don't you just stop? - What?</font>

887
00:52:30,252 --> 00:52:34,052
<font color="yellow">You're selfish, but you pretend to be naive in front of others.</font>

888
00:52:34,652 --> 00:52:35,652
<font color="yellow">You hypocrite.</font>

889
00:52:35,652 --> 00:52:36,782
<font color="yellow">Gargoyle Eyes!</font>

890
00:52:37,182 --> 00:52:38,282
<font color="yellow">Why that...</font>

891
00:52:41,152 --> 00:52:45,422
<font color="yellow">Even if I was angry, I still shouldn't have called him that.</font>

892
00:52:47,352 --> 00:52:49,982
<font color="yellow">You made a big mistake, Na Yun Shil.</font>

893
00:52:51,022 --> 00:52:52,052
<font color="yellow">You fool.</font>

894
00:52:54,482 --> 00:52:56,552
<font color="yellow">- Sir! - Help!</font>

895
00:52:57,122 --> 00:52:58,352
<font color="yellow">Move!</font>

896
00:53:02,722 --> 00:53:05,182
<font color="yellow">- Here! - Sir!</font>

897
00:53:06,052 --> 00:53:09,722
<font color="yellow">But still, he won't be mean to his life-saver, will he?</font>

898
00:53:09,822 --> 00:53:11,022
<font color="yellow">Are you in there?</font>

899
00:53:12,652 --> 00:53:14,022
<font color="yellow">Why don't you pick up the phone?</font>

900
00:53:15,752 --> 00:53:17,182
<font color="yellow">Were you going to eat ramyeon?</font>

901
00:53:18,052 --> 00:53:20,282
<font color="yellow">I was bringing you saengtae jjigae, but you didn't answer.</font>

902
00:53:20,382 --> 00:53:22,852
<font color="yellow">- So I just came in. - The phone didn't ring.</font>

903
00:53:24,482 --> 00:53:25,982
<font color="yellow">Oh, my bag.</font>

904
00:53:26,922 --> 00:53:30,182
<font color="yellow">I must have left it at work.</font>

905
00:53:30,282 --> 00:53:33,622
<font color="yellow">Where's your head at? Take this.</font>

906
00:53:34,922 --> 00:53:36,582
<font color="yellow">- Thank you. - Bye.</font>

907
00:53:39,722 --> 00:53:41,982
<font color="yellow">I'll have to go back to the shop.</font>

908
00:53:59,052 --> 00:54:00,182
<font color="yellow">Here it is.</font>

909
00:54:12,652 --> 00:54:13,952
<font color="yellow">Why is that down there?</font>

910
00:54:24,052 --> 00:54:25,682
<font color="yellow">What's he doing here?</font>

911
00:55:25,282 --> 00:55:31,952
<font color="yellow">(Wolgyesu Tailor Shop)</font>

912
00:55:37,022 --> 00:55:39,752
<font color="yellow">Mum's waiting for me. Get straight to the point.</font>

913
00:55:40,982 --> 00:55:42,652
<font color="yellow">You hurt my pride.</font>

914
00:55:43,752 --> 00:55:45,552
<font color="yellow">I've been thinking.</font>

915
00:55:46,552 --> 00:55:49,122
<font color="yellow">I know I'm the one who said we should get a divorce first,</font>

916
00:55:49,382 --> 00:55:52,222
