917
00:55:52,852 --> 00:55:55,022
<font color="yellow">It makes me feel like...</font>

918
00:55:55,882 --> 00:55:57,952
<font color="yellow">I'm the one who got divorced, not you.</font>

919
00:55:59,052 --> 00:56:00,252
<font color="yellow">What did you expect?</font>

920
00:56:01,122 --> 00:56:02,882
<font color="yellow">Did you think I would beg you not to divorce me?</font>

921
00:56:02,982 --> 00:56:04,452
<font color="yellow">I didn't expect you to beg.</font>

922
00:56:05,252 --> 00:56:07,522
<font color="yellow">But I didn't know you would end things so easily.</font>

923
00:56:10,952 --> 00:56:12,582
<font color="yellow">Am I no use to you...</font>

924
00:56:14,482 --> 00:56:16,152
<font color="yellow">now that my dad died?</font>

925
00:56:17,152 --> 00:56:18,252
<font color="yellow">Is that it?</font>

926
00:56:19,552 --> 00:56:21,322
<font color="yellow">Is that why you were willing to give up so easily?</font>

927
00:56:21,722 --> 00:56:23,382
<font color="yellow">I did everything you wanted me to.</font>

928
00:56:24,022 --> 00:56:25,852
<font color="yellow">It looks like that still hurt your pride.</font>

929
00:56:26,652 --> 00:56:29,722
<font color="yellow">How dare you hurt my pride.</font>

