934
00:56:40,552 --> 00:56:43,282
<font color="yellow">Sure, I used to be like that, too.</font>

935
00:56:43,982 --> 00:56:45,582
<font color="yellow">But I don't want to live like that any more.</font>

936
00:56:46,852 --> 00:56:50,652
<font color="yellow">I didn't have the luxury to care for your pride.</font>

937
00:56:51,252 --> 00:56:52,882
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry if I hurt you.</font>

938
00:56:53,422 --> 00:56:54,852
<font color="yellow">You seem drunk, so go home.</font>

939
00:56:55,052 --> 00:56:56,152
<font color="yellow">You horrible man.</font>

940
00:56:56,852 --> 00:56:58,022
<font color="yellow">You cruel man.</font>

941
00:56:59,982 --> 00:57:01,152
<font color="yellow">Get it together.</font>

942
00:57:02,452 --> 00:57:03,552
<font color="yellow">Listen to me carefully.</font>

943
00:57:04,052 --> 00:57:06,122
<font color="yellow">You being like this won't work any more.</font>

944
00:57:06,222 --> 00:57:07,452
<font color="yellow">We're strangers now.</font>

945
00:57:08,452 --> 00:57:10,652
<font color="yellow">We have nothing to do with each other now, okay?</font>

946
00:57:15,382 --> 00:57:16,422
<font color="yellow">Hey.</font>

947
00:57:17,052 --> 00:57:18,152
<font color="yellow">Hey, wake up.</font>

948
00:57:19,052 --> 00:57:20,052
<font color="yellow">Hyo Joo.</font>

949
00:57:26,752 --> 00:57:27,752
<font color="yellow">Who's there?</font>

950
00:57:34,552 --> 00:57:35,652
<font color="yellow">It's me.</font>

951
00:57:37,282 --> 00:57:38,422
<font color="yellow">What are you doing here?</font>

952
00:57:39,052 --> 00:57:41,682
