00:57:48,752 --> 00:57:49,922
<font color="yellow">Hey, Tae Yang.</font>

956
00:57:50,382 --> 00:57:52,622
<font color="yellow">I'll call you back later.</font>

957
00:57:53,322 --> 00:57:54,482
<font color="yellow">Yes, I'm sorry.</font>

958
00:57:56,352 --> 00:57:59,422
<font color="yellow">Why were you down there and listening to our conversation?</font>

959
00:57:59,582 --> 00:58:00,982
<font color="yellow">What do you think you're doing?</font>

960
00:58:01,852 --> 00:58:04,452
<font color="yellow">I know this can be misleading,</font>

961
00:58:05,152 --> 00:58:06,882
<font color="yellow">but I didn't do it on purpose.</font>

962
00:58:08,152 --> 00:58:09,852
<font color="yellow">I left my bag at work.</font>

963
00:58:10,222 --> 00:58:13,182
<font color="yellow">I just happened to be at the wrong place at a wrong time.</font>

964
00:58:14,182 --> 00:58:16,182
<font color="yellow">I know it's none of my business.</font>

965
00:58:16,452 --> 00:58:19,152
<font color="yellow">Why would I eavesdrop on a domestic dispute?</font>

966
00:58:19,382 --> 00:58:20,882
<font color="yellow">I'm not an idle person like that.</font>

967
00:58:20,982 --> 00:58:23,882
<font color="yellow">Whatever. I really don't like you.</font>

968
00:58:43,882 --> 00:58:46,152
<font color="yellow">Drive safely.</font>

969
00:59:03,122 --> 00:59:05,022
<font color="yellow">I just can't stop getting myself in trouble, can I?</font>

970
00:59:05,952 --> 00:59:07,722
<font color="yellow">Why am I like this?</font>

971
00:59:10,422 --> 00:59:11,622
<font color="yellow">Oh, I almost forgot.</font>

972
00:59:13,052 --> 00:59:14,752
<font color="yellow">Did I call you at a bad time?</font>

973
00:59:14,852 --> 00:59:17,922
<font color="yellow">Not at all. I just had to talk to someone.</font>

974
00:59:18,582 --> 00:59:20,682
<font color="yellow">- Where are you? - I'm at work.</font>

975
00:59:22,282 --> 00:59:23,482
<font color="yellow">Hey, Yun Shil.</font>

976
00:59:24,452 --> 00:59:25,482
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

977
00:59:27,822 --> 00:59:29,452
<font color="yellow">Don't forget to eat.</font>

978
00:59:30,052 --> 00:59:31,052
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

979
00:59:32,482 --> 00:59:33,982
<font color="yellow">I was just calling to check on you.</font>

980
00:59:34,552 --> 00:59:36,282
<font color="yellow">It's been long since I heard your voice.</font>

981
00:59:36,752 --> 00:59:38,052
<font color="yellow">Okay, get some rest.</font>

982
00:59:42,222 --> 00:59:44,022
<font color="yellow">I didn't even pay her back from last time.</font>

983
00:59:44,022 --> 00:59:46,952
<font color="yellow">I can't ask for more money.</font>

984
00:59:47,222 --> 00:59:50,752
<font color="yellow">Everyone, get back to work. Start moving.</font>

985
00:59:50,852 --> 00:59:54,182
<font color="yellow">Mr Kang. Go back to your station.</font>

986
00:59:54,182 --> 00:59:55,322
<font color="yellow">Yes, on my way.</font>

987
00:59:56,122 --> 00:59:59,252
<font color="yellow">The traffic is so heavy. I'm on my way.</font>

988
00:59:59,352 --> 01:00:00,582
<font color="yellow">You brat.</font>

