997
01:00:54,052 --> 01:00:55,322
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about?</font>

998
01:00:56,182 --> 01:00:58,522
<font color="yellow">I thought hard about the decision.</font>

999
01:00:59,352 --> 01:01:00,352
<font color="yellow">Please allow it, Mum.</font>

1000
01:01:00,352 --> 01:01:02,852
<font color="yellow">I'm guessing you're doing this...</font>

