01:01:03,052 --> 01:01:05,552
<font color="yellow">because you feel responsible for your dad leaving home.</font>

1002
01:01:05,652 --> 01:01:07,052
<font color="yellow">But it's not your fault.</font>

1003
01:01:07,352 --> 01:01:11,152
<font color="yellow">It had nothing to do with you. He did it on his own will.</font>

1004
01:01:11,252 --> 01:01:12,582
<font color="yellow">It's not because of him.</font>

1005
01:01:13,252 --> 01:01:15,052
<font color="yellow">I want to be happy.</font>

1006
01:01:15,552 --> 01:01:16,822
<font color="yellow">What are you saying?</font>

1007
01:01:17,322 --> 01:01:19,722
<font color="yellow">I've been working non-stop for a successful career.</font>

1008
01:01:20,652 --> 01:01:21,982
<font color="yellow">But I'm a mess now.</font>

1009
01:01:22,882 --> 01:01:24,682
<font color="yellow">I'm tired of competition and deception.</font>

1010
01:01:25,222 --> 01:01:27,322
<font color="yellow">I don't want to abandon my family for money.</font>

1011
01:01:27,682 --> 01:01:29,982
<font color="yellow">I'm tired of all that. I can't do it any more.</font>

1012
01:01:30,522 --> 01:01:35,382
<font color="yellow">But still, you're my perfect son.</font>

1013
01:01:35,582 --> 01:01:36,782
<font color="yellow">On top of getting a divorce,</font>

1014
01:01:36,782 --> 01:01:39,582
<font color="yellow">you're going to make suits for the rest of your life?</font>

1015
01:01:39,982 --> 01:01:42,222
<font color="yellow">That's not how I raised you.</font>

1016
01:01:43,222 --> 01:01:44,682
<font color="yellow">I can't allow it.</font>

1017
01:01:45,322 --> 01:01:47,052
<font color="yellow">Don't you think you should go in there, Dong Sook?</font>

1018
01:01:47,282 --> 01:01:50,652
<font color="yellow">Leave them be. They need some alone time together.</font>

1019
01:01:51,552 --> 01:01:53,352
