1020
01:01:53,352 --> 01:01:55,952
<font color="yellow">I am here.</font>

1021
01:01:57,652 --> 01:01:58,852
<font color="yellow">Susanna.</font>

1022
01:01:58,952 --> 01:02:01,052
<font color="yellow">Why did he get so drunk?</font>

