01:02:01,422 --> 01:02:02,552
<font color="yellow">Sung Jun.</font>

1024
01:02:03,552 --> 01:02:05,222
<font color="yellow">Oh, gosh.</font>

1025
01:02:05,422 --> 01:02:07,182
<font color="yellow">- Susanna. - It's not here.</font>

1026
01:02:07,522 --> 01:02:08,622
<font color="yellow">- Not here. - Oh, I see.</font>

1027
01:02:08,722 --> 01:02:10,452
<font color="yellow">What's wrong with him this time?</font>

1028
01:02:11,582 --> 01:02:13,652
<font color="yellow">He must've gotten free drinks from somewhere.</font>

1029
01:02:14,952 --> 01:02:16,052
<font color="yellow">Here I am.</font>

1030
01:02:17,182 --> 01:02:19,752
<font color="yellow">- My precious - I'll take that.</font>

1031
01:02:21,722 --> 01:02:23,052
<font color="yellow">Lay down.</font>

