1035
01:02:46,482 --> 01:02:47,482
<font color="yellow">Oh, my.</font>

1036
01:02:51,722 --> 01:02:55,552
<font color="yellow">How did he end up like this?</font>

1037
01:03:05,052 --> 01:03:06,352
<font color="yellow">Eat it while it's still hot.</font>

1038
01:03:21,052 --> 01:03:22,852
<font color="yellow">You may have your reasons,</font>

1039
01:03:23,152 --> 01:03:26,882
<font color="yellow">but you working at the tailor shop is the last thing I want.</font>

1040
01:03:27,182 --> 01:03:30,982
<font color="yellow">I still can't get over the fact that my son got a divorce.</font>

1041
01:03:31,352 --> 01:03:34,052
