1042
01:03:34,252 --> 01:03:36,582
<font color="yellow">Don't you pity me?</font>

1043
01:03:38,422 --> 01:03:42,152
<font color="yellow">- I'm sorry. - Then don't do it.</font>

1044
01:03:42,822 --> 01:03:44,022
<font color="yellow">Eat up.</font>

1045
01:03:55,622 --> 01:03:57,982
<font color="yellow">Slow down. You don't want it going down the wrong pipe.</font>

1046
01:03:59,052 --> 01:04:02,552
<font color="yellow">I haven't had a meal in peace for so long.</font>

1047
01:04:04,882 --> 01:04:08,722
<font color="yellow">Is that how you've been all along?</font>

1048
01:04:10,182 --> 01:04:13,722
<font color="yellow">I should have come to you sooner.</font>

1049
01:04:14,752 --> 01:04:17,982
<font color="yellow">I was stupid not to.</font>

1050
01:04:22,252 --> 01:04:23,882
<font color="yellow">Eat up.</font>

1051
01:04:25,052 --> 01:04:26,122
<font color="yellow">Eat.</font>

