1069
01:05:52,882 --> 01:05:53,982
<font color="yellow">I don't need it.</font>

1070
01:05:54,352 --> 01:05:56,552
<font color="yellow">- Listen to me carefully. - Yes, Mr Lee.</font>

1071
01:05:56,752 --> 01:05:59,222
<font color="yellow">As of today, you're fired.</font>

1072
