1082
01:06:58,722 --> 01:07:00,052
<font color="yellow">Is he really going to work at the tailor shop?</font>

1083
01:07:00,052 --> 01:07:02,982
<font color="yellow">You need a wife to get your coat, not your mother.</font>

1084
01:07:02,982 --> 01:07:05,582
<font color="yellow">I'm figuring out how to make myself happy.</font>

1085
01:07:05,582 --> 01:07:06,822
